<bibRefCitation id="EFF74B0FFFE6FF8EFE47F9F9FD502415" author="Canu" box="[453,717,1586,1611]" pageId="4" pageNumber="475" refString="Canu, F. &amp; Bassler, R. S. (1923) North American later Tertiary and Quaternary Bryozoa. Bulletin of the United States National Museum, 125, i - viii, 1 - 302, 47 pls." type="journal article" year="1923">Canu &amp; Bassler, 1923</bibRefCitation>
